<paragraph blockId="68.[264,1323,1213,1639]" box="[312,1252,1493,1519]" pageId="68" pageNumber="69">
Etymology. Latin 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Scarbrough Table Of Contents" authorityYear="2005" box="[524,591,1493,1518]" class="Insecta" family="Asilidae" genus="Afroestricus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="68" pageNumber="69" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="vorax">
<emphasis box="[524,591,1493,1518]" italics="true" pageId="68" pageNumber="69">vorax</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
for vicious, referring to the predaceous habits of asilids.
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="68.[264,1323,1213,1639]" pageId="68" pageNumber="69">
Remarks. 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Scarbrough Table Of Contents" authorityYear="2005" box="[433,651,1533,1558]" class="Insecta" family="Asilidae" genus="Afroestricus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="68" pageNumber="69" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="vorax">
<emphasis box="[433,651,1533,1558]" italics="true" pageId="68" pageNumber="69">Afroestricus vorax</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
is similar to 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Scarbrough Table Of Contents" authorityYear="2005" box="[812,938,1533,1558]" class="Insecta" family="Asilidae" genus="Afroestricus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="68" pageNumber="69" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="sankofa">
<emphasis box="[812,938,1533,1558]" italics="true" pageId="68" pageNumber="69">A. sankofa</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
and 
<taxonomicName box="[1000,1121,1533,1558]" class="Insecta" family="Asilidae" genus="Afroestricus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="68" pageNumber="69" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="vittatus">
<emphasis box="[1000,1121,1533,1558]" italics="true" pageId="68" pageNumber="69">A. vittatus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
in the unusually thick femora of the male, the stout posteroventral bristle on the middle femora of both sexes but is distinguished from them by the characters of the terminalia (
<figureCitation box="[1117,1287,1613,1639]" captionStart="FIGURES 187–192" captionStartId="68.[264,383,1095,1119]" captionTargetBox="[429,1176,447,1073]" captionTargetId="figure-231@68.[417,1191,437,1087]" captionTargetPageId="68" captionText="FIGURES 187–192. Afroestricus vorax, sp. n. Male terminalia: 187–189. Lateral, dorsal, and ventral views. 190. Gonostylus. 191–192. Aedeagus, dorsal and lateral views." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5050675" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/5050675/files/figure.png" pageId="68" pageNumber="69">Figs. 187–192</figureCitation>
).
</paragraph>
